page.title: 16Famous Residents Now
page.content: We have not found anyone really famous but several are well-known in their particular fields.{SIR A.T.BARNARD}, .B.,O.B.E.Born 1893.Chartered Engineer who became Chief Superintendant,Royal Ordnance Factories, Woolwich.Knighted 1958. {JANE.L.FINLAY},J.P.Born 1917. Trained as teacher but has had varied career.1980 Deputy Chairman of Equal Oportunities Commission.{BARON A.R. MAIS},J.P.,O.B.E.,G.B.E.Born 1911. Military career and varied business interests.Life Peer 1967.Lord Mayor of London,1972-1973.{DR G.OSTLERE pen- name RICHARD GORDON},author of comedy"Doctor" series.{MARTIN RUSSELL}. Once journalist now crime novelist.{BARON WILLIS OF CHISLEHURST}.Born 1918.Playwright. Well known for Dixon of Dock Green T.V. scripts.Life Peer 1963.
